03:43.812 --> 03:45.812
It's not a good idea.

03:46.982 --> 03:49.399
- What? 
- You going up there to see Lori.

03:49.451 --> 03:51.318
Madison doesn't know what it's like

03:51.320 --> 03:53.036
to be lied to for all those years.

03:53.072 --> 03:54.238
It's not just about what Madison said.

03:54.290 --> 03:56.990
Carter, I know how much Lori meant to you.

03:56.992 --> 03:58.825
You don't owe her anything.

03:58.878 --> 04:00.294
She's not your responsibility.

04:00.329 --> 04:03.163
Look, the doctor just wants
to ask me some questions, okay?

04:03.165 --> 04:05.132
Maybe I could tell him
something that would help her.

04:05.167 --> 04:06.550
I get that.

04:06.585 --> 04:08.385
Would you take me?

04:08.420 --> 04:10.837
If that's what you want.

04:15.261 --> 04:17.511
Yeah, that's what I want.

04:18.930 --> 04:21.098
Why does it look like a beauty pageant

04:21.149 --> 04:22.432
blew up in my house?

04:22.484 --> 04:23.567
Um, fundraiser?

04:23.602 --> 04:25.652
Charity fundraiser at the country club

04:25.688 --> 04:26.937
this afternoon, you remember?

04:26.989 --> 04:28.572
I completely forgot.

04:28.607 --> 04:30.607
Well, it's been a little nuts around here.

04:30.659 --> 04:34.027
Taylor told me that crazy
has reared her head yet again?

04:34.079 --> 04:36.163
I mean, what was that woman thinking?

04:36.198 --> 04:37.698
Can you imagine doing something like that?

04:37.750 --> 04:40.167
- Thankfully, no. 
- You guys are never gonna believe this.

04:40.202 --> 04:42.869
- What? 
- Max just called me.

04:42.871 --> 04:44.087
He and Carter are on their way

04:44.123 --> 04:46.506
to the mental hospital
to talk to Lori's doctor.

04:46.542 --> 04:48.375
What? No, I talked to Carter this morning.

04:48.377 --> 04:50.677
She wasn't even thinking about doing that.

04:50.713 --> 04:52.679
Well, now she is.

04:52.715 --> 04:53.964
Voicemail.

04:54.016 --> 04:55.299
Carter, it's me.

04:55.351 --> 04:57.884
Please, when you get
this, will you call me?

04:57.886 --> 04:59.553
I'm worried.

04:59.605 --> 05:02.105
- Where's your dad? 
- He went to the office.

05:02.141 --> 05:03.807
Honey, I am so sorry,
but I don't think that

05:03.859 --> 05:05.309
- I can do this today. 
- What?

05:05.361 --> 05:06.944
- I'm chair of the committee.
- I understand that,

05:06.979 --> 05:09.896
but I think that we need to
go up there and be with Carter.

05:09.949 --> 05:11.732
- I'm sorry. 
- No.

05:11.784 --> 05:13.150
No, Lori doesn't get to do this.

05:13.202 --> 05:16.570
She doesn't get to stop our lives

05:16.622 --> 05:18.782
every time she does something crazy.

05:18.807 --> 05:20.705
She's right... otherwise, we're
just playing right into her hands.

05:20.730 --> 05:22.588
But this isn't about Lori.

05:22.613 --> 05:24.195
This is about Carter.

05:24.730 --> 05:27.147
Carter didn't ask you to come.

05:27.182 --> 05:29.099
She didn't even tell you she was going.

05:30.562 --> 05:34.070
Mom, I'm sorry, I just...

05:34.094 --> 05:36.511
I made a commitment, and I'm not gonna

05:36.536 --> 05:39.537
disappoint people because of
something this crazy woman did.

05:42.707 --> 05:44.073
You're right.

05:45.543 --> 05:47.620
You're absolutely right.

05:47.645 --> 05:48.978
I'm sorry.

05:49.003 --> 05:50.553
You look beautiful.

05:50.578 --> 05:51.847
Thanks.

05:57.589 --> 05:59.171
(Lori, echoing) Carter.

05:59.173 --> 06:00.723
Carter...

06:03.061 --> 06:04.727
It's okay, mommy's here.

